from datetime import datetime

# Define the date
date_str = "2022-08-17"

# Convert the string to a datetime object
date_obj = datetime.strptime(date_str, "%Y-%m-%d")

# Get the weekday (0=Monday, 6=Sunday)
weekday = date_obj.strftime("%A")
weekday
